item.title: Idugeonpro Free?
item.dc:creator: @xryz xryz
item.description:
@xryz wrote:

as far as i know idungeonpro is for rsbuddy. i made a cracked one when it worked for PB. if i knew how/where rsbuddy stored/accessed the scripts i may be able to make one, but i would have to have the information to an account that already bought idungeonpro.

i would hope the script maker improved his method on keeping his scripts from getting cracked. i dont think i will try to cracked it again. if its working and its good, then pay the guy for his hard work. there is a open source dungeoneering script, so if u feel like trying to make a good script u can download it from rsbuddy. http://scripts.rsbuddy.com/?script=ArteDungeon that script kinda works. it got me through the first level, but it messed up on the second one and its the only free dungeoneering script from there that remotely worked.
